She listened to Rodimus as he mentioned a few things that were too close to 
her comfort about the past. Then the mention of the Pax Cybertronia. This made 
her curious. Much happened in the time of her stasis lock in the Decepticon 
Crypt.

As for the Warlords... he was right. Many a time had she been stuck in the 
middle. even a couple times made a warlord for some twisted purpose to 
manipulated or some petty plan.

But as to how ruthless he can be, she would enjoy seeing that. For to her, he 
would then end up to be like those he so desperately wanted to destroy. She 
smirked as her crimson optics watched Rodimus, standing at Hydras' side.

--part1_127.2c0b2257.2c2386a2_boundary
